alues":["fp8_fast 似乎会导致严重的质量下降。\nfp_16_fast 启用了最新版 PyTorch 夜间版本中可用的 “在 FP16 通用矩阵乘法（GEMMs）中进行全 FP16 累加” 功能，这大约能提升 20% 的速度。\n\nfp8_fast seems to cause huge quality degradation\nfp_16_fast enables \"Full FP16 Accmumulation in FP16 GEMMs\" feature available in the very latest pytorch nightly, this is around 20% speed boost. \nSageattn if you have it installed can be used for almost double inference speed"],"color":"#432","bgcolor":"#653"},{"id":53,"type":"Note","pos":[870,-930],"size":[340,310],"flags":{},"order":8,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[],"properties":{},"widgets_values":["TeaCache 可以被视为一种自动跳过步骤的工具。\n相对的 l1 阈值决定了这一过程的激进程度，数值越高速度越快，但质量受损也更严重。使用此模型时，绝对不能跳过最开始的步骤，否则会破坏运动效果。在使用预先计算好的系数时，阈值应比使用默认系数时高得多。\n\nTeaCache could be considered to be sort of an automated step skipper \nThe relative l1 threshold -value determines how aggressive this is, higher values are faster but quality suffers more. Very first steps should NEVER be skipped with this model or it kills the motion. When using the pre-calculated coefficients, the treshold value should be much higher than with the default coefficients."],"color":"#432","bgcolor":"#653"},{"id":54,"type":"Note","pos":[1290,-760],"size":[360,130],"flags":{},"order":9,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[],"properties":{},"widgets_values":["增强视频功能可以提高结果的保真度，但数值过高会导致结果出现噪点。\nEnhance-a-video can increase the fidelity of the results, too high values lead to noisy results."],"color":"#432","bgcolor":"#653"},{"id":42,"type":"Note","pos":[-550,-730],"size":[310,290],"flags":{},"order":10,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[],"properties":{},"widgets_values":["根据你的显存调整要交换的块，这是速度和内存使用之间的权衡。\n或者，还有一种选择是使用 DiffSynt-Studios 中引入的显存管理。这通常速度较慢，但与块交换相比，能节省更多的显存。\n\nAdjust the blocks to swap based on your VRAM, this is a tradeoff between speed and memory usage.\n\nAlternatively there's option to use VRAM management introduced in DiffSynt-Studios. This is usually slower, but saves even more VRAM compared to BlockSwap"],"color":"#432","bgcolor":"#653"},{"id":44,"type":"Note","pos":[-560,-1020],"size":[310,200],"flags":{},"order":11,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[],"properties":{},"widgets_values":["如果你已安装 Triton（注：本镜像已安装），连接此设备可提升约 30% 的速度。\nIf you have Triton installed, connect this for ~30% speed increase"],"color":"#432","bgcolor":"#653"},{"id":58,"type":"LoadImage","pos":[-610,40],"size":[413.10479736328125,498.3180847167969],"flags":{},"order":12,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"localized_name":"图像","name":"image","type":"COMBO","widget":{"name":"image"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"选择文件上传","name":"upload","type":"IMAGEUPLOAD","widget":{"name":"upload"},"link":null}],"outputs":[{"label":"图像","localized_name":"图像","name":"IMAGE","type":"IMAGE","links":[72]},{"label":"遮罩","localized_name":"遮罩","name":"MASK","type":"MASK","links":null}],"properties":{"cnr_id":"comfy-core","ver":"0.3.26","Node name for S&R":"LoadImage"},"widgets_values":["input.webp","image"],"color":"#2a363b","bgcolor":"#3f5159"},{"id":16,"type":"WanVideoTextEncode","pos":[890,-450],"size":[340,440],"flags":{},"order":26,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"label":"t5","localized_name":"t5","name":"t5","shape":7,"type":"WANTEXTENCODER","link":15},{"label":"待卸载模型","localized_name":"模型卸载","name":"model_to_offload","shape":7,"type":"WANVIDEOMODEL","link":79},{"label":"正向提示","localized_name":"正面提示","name":"positive_prompt","type":"STRING","widget":{"name":"positive_prompt"},"link":null},{"label":"负向提示","localized_name":"负面提示","name":"negative_prompt","type":"STRING","widget":{"name":"negative_prompt"},"link":null},{"label":"强制卸载","localized_name":"强制卸载","name":"force_offload","shape":7,"type":"BOOLEAN","widget":{"name":"force_offload"},"link":null},{"label":"使用磁盘缓存","localized_name":"使用磁盘缓存","name":"use_disk_cache","shape":7,"type":"BOOLEAN","widget":{"name":"use_disk_cache"},"link":null},{"label":"设备","localized_name":"设备","name":"device","shape":7,"type":"COMBO","widget":{"name":"device"},"link":null}],"outputs":[{"label":"文本嵌入","localized_name":"文本嵌入","name":"text_embeds","